abstract: Baseball Roundup; Los Angeles Angels defeat Houston Astros, 6-5; other MLB scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Los Angeles took two of three in the series and pulled to a game and a half behind Houston.

headline.main: Angels Rally Past Astros, Climbing Toward a Wild-Card Spot
